flow.BPMNXML:
<definitions typeLanguage="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" expressionLanguage="http://www.w3.org/1999/XPath" targetNamespace="http://www.activiti.org/test"

    xmlns:omgdi="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI">
    <process id="schedulerdemo" name="Scheduler Demo" isExecutable="true">
        <startEvent id="startevent1" name="Start"/>
        <userTask id="usertask1" name="Question1" activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}" activiti:formKey="poi_Question1_FormId"/>
        <endEvent id="endevent1" name="End"/>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow1" sourceRef="startevent1" targetRef="usertask2"/>
        <userTask id="usertask2" name="Question2" activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}" activiti:formKey="poi_Question2_FormId"/>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow3" sourceRef="usertask2" targetRef="servicetask1"/>
        <userTask id="usertask3" name="Answer1" activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}" activiti:formKey="poi_Answer1_FormId"/>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow4" sourceRef="usertask1" targetRef="parallelgateway1"/>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow5" sourceRef="usertask3" targetRef="endevent1"/>
        <parallelGateway id="parallelgateway1" name="Parallel Gateway"/>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow6" sourceRef="parallelgateway1" targetRef="usertask3"/>
        <userTask id="usertask4" name="Scheduler" activiti:assignee="tpanagos@point.io" activiti:formKey="poi_Helper_FormId"/>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow7" sourceRef="parallelgateway1" targetRef="usertask4"/>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow8" sourceRef="usertask4" targetRef="endevent1"/>
        <serviceTask id="servicetask1" name="IT Center Interface" activiti:class="plugins.facts">
            <extensionElements>
                <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
                    <activiti:string>poi_gettobe_fact</activiti:string>
                </activiti:field>
                <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
                    <activiti:expression>${getMap}</activiti:expression>
                </activiti:field>
            </extensionElements>
        </serviceTask>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow9" sourceRef="servicetask1" targetRef="usertask1"/>
    </process>
    <bpmndi:BPMNDiagram id="BPMNDiagram_template1">
        <bpmndi:BPMNPlane bpmnElement="template1" id="BPMNPlane_template1">
            <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="startevent1" id="BPMNShape_startevent1">
                <omgdc:Bounds height="35.0" width="35.0" x="30.0" y="90.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
            <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="usertask1" id="BPMNShape_usertask1">
                <omgdc:Bounds height="55.0" width="105.0" x="286.0" y="80.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
            <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="endevent1" id="BPMNShape_endevent1">

            <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="parallelgateway1" id="BPMNShape_parallelgateway1">

            <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="usertask4" id="BPMNShape_usertask4">

            </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
            <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="servicetask1" id="BPMNShape_servicetask1">

            </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
            <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow1" id="BPMNEdge_flow1">

            </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
            <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow3" id="BPMNEdge_flow3">
                <omgdi:waypoint x="152.0" y="135.0"/>

            </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
            <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow4" id="BPMNEdge_flow4">

            </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
            <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow8" id="BPMNEdge_flow8">

        </bpmndi:BPMNPlane>
